    <item>
      <title>白宫撤回拜登关于委内瑞拉大选的评论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/white-house-walks-back-biden-comment-on-venezuela-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫周四撤回了总统乔·拜登关于委内瑞拉举行重新选举的建议，此前该言论引发了人们对美国对 7 月选举的立场的质疑。美国一直表示，尼古拉斯·马杜罗政权操纵了委内瑞拉选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/white-house-walks-back-biden-comment-on-venezuela-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 20:28:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国放宽对 Aukus 与澳大利亚、英国联盟的出口管制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/us-eases-export-controls-for-aukus-alliance-with-australia-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登总统的政府已确定澳大利亚和英国拥有与美国相当的出口管制体系，以满足 Aukus 伙伴关系下简化武器贸易的一项关键要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/us-eases-export-controls-for-aukus-alliance-with-australia-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国农业部寻求放宽绿色燃料农作物使用规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/usda-seeks-easier-rules-for-crops-to-be-used-in-green-jet-fuel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国农业部部长汤姆·维尔萨克表示，美国农业部正在推动放宽用于生产可再生燃料的农作物的税收抵免要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/usda-seeks-easier-rules-for-crops-to-be-used-in-green-jet-fuel</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 19:09:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰宣布俄军投降 为战争最大投降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/ukraine-reports-largest-surrender-by-russian-troops-of-the-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰军队称，他们接受了自两年多前战争开始以来最大规模的俄罗斯士兵投降，而基辅军方则声称将继续扩大跨境入侵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/ukraine-reports-largest-surrender-by-russian-troops-of-the-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 14:39:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列与伊朗紧张局势升温，加沙停火谈判在多哈开启</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/gaza-truce-talks-start-in-doha-as-israel-iran-tensions-simmer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列开始与国际调解员进行谈判，商讨暂停已持续 10 个多月的加沙战争的提议，以缓解这个犹太国家与伊朗之间不断升级的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/gaza-truce-talks-start-in-doha-as-israel-iran-tensions-simmer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 13:49:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称赞哈里斯，称她“会成为一位出色的总统”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/biden-returns-to-campaign-trail-navigating-new-harris-dynamic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登重返竞选之路，面临着一个奇怪而又苦乐参半的局面：如何从现任总统候选人转变为副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的宣传推手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/biden-returns-to-campaign-trail-navigating-new-harris-dynamic</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国药品价格措施将在 2026 年降低 75 亿美元成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/us-drug-price-negotiations-cut-costs-7-5-billion-in-first-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府表示，美国政府具有里程碑意义的药品价格谈判将在其成立第一年为美国人节省75亿美元，这是降低其全球最高药品费用的第一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/us-drug-price-negotiations-cut-costs-7-5-billion-in-first-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
